data.description: Totally renovated "smart home" bungalow in a great location just minutes from SLU and walking distance to Cherokee Street. Nest thermostat, Google Nest doorbell,Yale lock, high end finishes throughout. All new HVAC, Plumbing & Electrical. Beautiful, neutral wood flooring. Total open concept with gorgeous kitchen offering large island, pendant lights, granite countertops and stainless appliances. Perfect for entertaining. A full, dry basement awaits your finishes. Add another bedroom and or bath. This home also has a beautiful detached garage. Move right in and make this your home!
